{"tid":85270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人仔狂升!! 想問下 diu7支那 死在去邊?","createTime":"2017-01-18T08:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T09:56:27.000Z","uid":42031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"699a47771ed4457f042102f5bd8b7eb9ee72f1d8","tid":85270,"uid":42031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:08:21.000Z","msg":"人民幣兌美元匯率中間價今天報6.8525，較前一個交易日升值4.67分。<br />\n<br />\n前一日人民幣中間價報6.8992，下調1.18分。<br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行授權中國外匯交易中心公布，18日銀行間外匯市場人民幣匯率中間價為，1美元兌人民幣6.8525元，升值467個基點（4.67分）。<br />\n<br />\n對於人民幣未來的走勢，專家看法分歧。匯豐外幣策略環球主管潘達維向中國證券網表示，今年人民幣整體呈現出貶值的趨勢，但貶值幅度較小，最低可能將貶至7.2關口。<br />\n<br />\n國際金融問題專家趙慶明則指出，隨著美元強勢逐漸結束，人民幣兌美元匯率有可能出現總體升值態勢。他估計今年人民幣對美元匯率的波動會在6.60到7.0關口之間，跌破7.0的可能性相對較小。1060118"},{"pid":"47b740e4de3870c2424e2f9dbacad5105824e23e","tid":85270,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:38:11.000Z","msg":"留名待笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cbe8ad45825b892057e9e68b35d59bb56aa73a","tid":85270,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:46:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/web_tc/main?pr=pns&amp;tab=s00004&amp;nodeid=1484675855663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fweb_tc%2Fmain%3Fpr%3Dpns%26tab%3Ds00004%26nodeid%3D1484675855663&d=E1%2FwOurwXdkpt3J7pKqlb0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=3c583399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fweb_tc%2Fmain%3Fpr%3Dpns%26tab%3Ds00004%26nodeid%3D1484675855663&h=ec3ea645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/web_tc/main?pr=pns&amp;tab=s00004&amp;nodeid=1484675855663</a><br />\n有乜感想？"},{"pid":"e6b078141b3920f3f84178da1d02a607fbd135d6","tid":85270,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:02:23.000Z","msg":"盈大地產去年虧損擴大至3.64億元 不派末期息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盈大地產(00432)公布, 去年虧損擴大至3億6400萬元, 每股虧損22.96仙, 不派末期息. 對比2015年虧損2億7300萬元.<br />\n<br />\n綜合收入增長半成, 至1億7400萬元. 毛利約1億1800萬元, 增加百分之6, 毛利率百分之68, 上升1個百分點.<br />\n<br />\n期內, 因為去年6月到期的認購差價期權公平值調整, 錄得6000萬元虧損."},{"pid":"ea1153817a7815cbc870b665d9d7ae7a9013c91a","tid":85270,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"龍源技術：2016年預虧約1.6億元 或連續兩年虧損<br />\n<br />\n證券時報網（<a href=\"http://www.stcn.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stcn.com&d=E1%2FwOurwXdkpt3J7pKqlb0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=4ecc9fd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.stcn.com</a>）01月13日訊<br />\n<br />\n龍源技術（300105） 1月13日晚間披露業績預告，公司2016年預計虧損1.61億元至1.66億元，2015年虧損4782.27萬元，或將連續兩年虧損。龍源技術表示，虧損原因為市場競爭日益加劇，市場規模萎縮以及營業收入結構的變化。"},{"pid":"78adb3ce89f7155cbceb38a16a90bb46ba640ec1","tid":85270,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"新華社深圳１月１８日電（記者趙瑞希）１８日，深交所創業板指低開後，呈震盪走勢，最終報收１８４５．７９點，較上一個交易日下跌２２．０８點，跌幅１．１８％。全日，創業板成交金額為４７０．９億元，比上個交易日減少１８１．４億元。<br />\n<br />\n創業板當日交易的５４４只股票中，收盤報跌的有４５４只。當日，創業板有８２只個股收盤報漲，其中新雷能、美聯新材。<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n咁多負面新聞，我唔知冥幣回升有咩用囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd55f62eb3809ff69fce039d9136b4fbfc574f6","tid":85270,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/web_tc/main?pr=pns&amp;tab=s00004&amp;nodeid=1484675855663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fweb_tc%2Fmain%3Fpr%3Dpns%26tab%3Ds00004%26nodeid%3D1484675855663&d=E1%2FwOurwXdkpt3J7pKqlb0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=3c583399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fweb_tc%2Fmain%3Fpr%3Dpns%26tab%3Ds00004%26nodeid%3D1484675855663&h=ec3ea645\" data-auto-lin